            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Dust your work surface with a generous sprinkling of <strong>flour</strong></p><p>Unwrap your <strong>puff pastry</strong> and roll it out to approx. 0.5cm thickness with a <strong>rolling pin</strong></p><p>Line a baking tray (or two!) with <strong>non-stick baking paper</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
