      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Spread your<strong> tomato paste </strong>evenly over the pastry with the back of a spoon, leaving a 1cm border around the edge</p><p>Sprinkle your <strong>dried thyme</strong> and <strong>half</strong> the <strong>grated Italian hard cheese </strong>(you'll use the rest later!) all over with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and top with the <strong>torn mozzarella</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
