      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the vegetables have slightly softened, add the <strong>stock</strong>,<strong> finely chopped tomatoes</strong> and 2 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong> to the pot with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Bring to the boil over a high heat and once boiling, reduce the heat to medium and cook for 11-12 min or until slightly thickened</p><p>Once slightly thickened, remove the pot from the heat and blitz until smooth with a <strong>(stick) blender</strong> – this is your <strong>tomato soup</strong></p>",
