        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>tomato soup </strong>topped with the <strong>remaining grated Italian hard cheese</strong>, a generous grind of <strong>black pepper </strong>and<strong> </strong>drizzle over your <strong>Henderson's Relish</strong> – this is your <strong>Henderson's tomato soup</strong></p><p>Tip: Not a fan of Henderson's? Just add a little!</p><p>Serve the <strong>cheesy pinwheels </strong>to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
